  "mainHtml": "\n<section class=\"case-hero\" style=\"--case-bg: url(/precision/end-to-end-quality-tracking.png)\">\n<div class=\"container case-hero-inner\">\n<div class=\"breadcrumb\"><a href=\"/\">首页</a><span>/</span><a href=\"/industries\">行业</a><span>/</span><a href=\"/industries/semiconductor\">半导体</a><span>/</span><b>行业案例</b></div>\n<span>半导体案例</span>\n<h1>设备定位夹具小批量加工</h1>\n<p>基准定位 / 检测治具 / 备件加工</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section case-detail-section\">\n<div class=\"container case-detail-layout\">\n<article class=\"case-story\">\n<div class=\"case-summary-grid\">\n<div><span>行业</span><strong>半导体</strong></div>\n<div><span>零件功能</span><strong>基准定位 / 检测治具 / 备件加工</strong></div>\n<div><span>制造能力</span><strong>精密CNC、洁净包装、平面度检测、批次追溯</strong></div>\n</div>\n<h2>项目场景</h2>\n<p>围绕机台定位、检测辅助和备件替换，控制基准面、孔位和平面度。</p>\n<h2>方案配置</h2>\n<div class=\"case-step-grid\">\n<div><b>01</b><strong>零件功能确认</strong><span>明确装配位置、受力方式、环境条件和验证目标。</span></div>\n<div><b>02</b><strong>工艺与材料匹配</strong><span>根据尺寸、公差、表面和批次要求组合制造能力。</span></div>\n<div><b>03</b><strong>检测与交付</strong><span>围绕关键尺寸、外观状态和装配反馈输出交付资料。</span></div>\n</div>\n<h2>交付结果</h2>\n<p>夹具小批量稳定交付，配套尺寸记录和批次信息。</p>\n</article>\n<aside class=\"case-aside\">\n<img alt=\"设备定位夹具小批量加工\" src=\"/precision/end-to-end-quality-tracking.png\"/>\n<h3>半导体制造能力</h3>\n<p>继续查看定位夹具、设备腔体和精密备件等半导体设备案例。</p>\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/industries/semiconductor\">返回半导体行业</a>\n<a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"/quote#quote-upload\">提交类似需求</a>\n</aside>\n</div>\n</section>\n"
